name: Amber Heard
description:
Amber Heard, famous Hollywood actress. With the departure of AICelebArt, I hope this will suffice.

The embed has been trained on SD 1.5 and works well on most 1.5 based models. Has a tendency to create monotone backgrounds on a few models, inpainting or strong prompting should solve this.

If you enjoy my creations and want to support me or have a face you'd like to commission, consider supporting me on Ko-Fi or Buy Me A Coffee :)
